              },
              "free_text": [
                " The errors include those arising from",
                "statistic and calibration."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Since the neutron capture targets employed emit",
                " also some secondary lines, although with low",
                " relative intensity with respect to the principal",
                " line, it is necessary to correct their contribution,",
                " solving a linear equation system of special type.",
                " Using the special equations presented by Caldwell",
                " the cross section measured have been recalculating",
                " for variation of the average number of neutrons as",
                " a function of the excitation energy."
              ]
            }
          ],
